iStore in Vodacom World is closing down, and is holding a “closing sale” – with up to 70% off items. The news follows an announcement by Vodacom that its Vodacom World campus would undergo a massive revamp from 17 March until late 2018. The iStore deals are available from iStore Vodacom World and while stocks last. A selection of the deals available are shown below, with more deals available in-store. 